  "title": "refactoring(highlight): refactor highlighting into a widget and connector",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR adds a new Highlight widget for the react-dom users and a connector for other flavours of react. The underlying parsing function now transforms the highlighted attribute into a  intermediary agnostic structure: `[{value: string, isHighlighted}, {value: string, isHighlighted}, ...]`\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\nThe highlighter can now be used as a component which is more convenient and we can easily use it for react-native. The widget and the connector are documented, and the getting started and examples are up to date.\r\n\r\nSide note: I also updated the connector layout to conditionally add examples if some exist.",
